{"tid":1773000,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民陣明遊行 籲前線警克制","createTime":"2019-12-07T06:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T08:53:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3a8d9cd67a9f315f438cc0697d0d3abeaa31dbaf","tid":1773000,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:14:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191207/SXWN4Q2UJVCNFKB7ZIHLPOW4MM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191207%2FSXWN4Q2UJVCNFKB7ZIHLPOW4MM%2F&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRHaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=6e737d5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191207%2FSXWN4Q2UJVCNFKB7ZIHLPOW4MM%2F&h=c4611b4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191207/SXWN4Q2UJVCNFKB7ZIHLPOW4MM/</a><br />\n<br />\n民陣明遊行 籲前線警克制<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【聲討極權】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民陣明日在港島發起12.8「國際人權日遊行」，是民陣四個多月來首次再獲警方發出不反對通知書。民主派呼籲上街，向林鄭月娥政府表明市民不會接受假貨獨立檢討委員會。但警方警告遊行若被暴力騎劫，將會腰斬。而民陣則呼籲前線警員「做番紀律部隊應有嘅模樣」。<br />\n<br />\n民陣發起12.8遊行將在明天下午2時在維園中央草坪集合，3時出發，經高士威道、怡和街、軒尼詩道、金鐘道、德輔道中，以中環遮打道行人專用區為終點。民陣指出，如人數太多會提早出發，市民如不想入維園，可於波斯富街以後路段中途加入。民陣人員會在沿途各區行人天橋上點算參加人數，市民若不想行至終點，應至少行完一區。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191207/large/1575648664_9ef0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191207%2Flarge%2F1575648664_9ef0.gif&h=594be054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明日將在港島舉行國際人權日遊行，上一次民陣辦遊行獲發不反對通知書已是7月21日。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不接受假貨獨立檢討委員會<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：飛行服務隊 懲教 受累評分跌<br />\n<br />\n民陣召集人岑子杰呼籲曾在區議會選舉中投票的市民都參加遊行，向林鄭月娥政府展示「香港人唔係選舉完就算，完咗選舉我哋仍會喺街頭發聲」，堅持五大訴求，決不接受無法定調查權力的獨立檢討委員會。<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰相信遊行能和平進行，現時警民關係跌至冰點，民陣會盡量負起緩衝角色。警方高層曾表示若遊行人數眾多，會開放更多路面，希望前線警員克制，「做番紀律部隊應有嘅模樣」。不少民主派候任區議員都會參加遊行，已有人告誡他們「千祈唔好俾警察拉咗，俾建制派翻盤」。岑子杰亦相信勇武前線能放亦能收，有智慧判斷如何行動。但中止遊行權在警方，他呼籲港鐵周日不要暫停服務，以免令市民無法離開。沿途各政黨的街站亦會協助疏散參加者。<br />\n<br />\n對於警務處長鄧炳強呼籲民陣拿出勇氣譴責暴力，岑子杰指出，警方濫用暴力及濫射催淚彈已造成人道災難，「我哋無可能看不見欺凌者嘅暴力，去指摘反抗者所使用嘅武力」。他希望鄧炳強比前任處長盧偉聰更有良知及智慧，拿勇氣譴責警暴，「欠缺良心同智慧嘅勇氣，只係愚勇」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191207/large/1575648663_3fa4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191207%2Flarge%2F1575648663_3fa4.gif&h=cd8b66b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岑子杰（前排左二）昨與民主派出席記者會，呼籲市民上街表達訴求。李家皓攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191207/large/1575648664_1774.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191207%2Flarge%2F1575648664_1774.gif&h=bf0a0cab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">遊行於明日下午2時在維園集合，3時出發，以中環遮打道行人專用區為終點。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警：有暴力事件或腰斬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港島總區高級警司（行動）吳樂俊昨在記者會上指出，過去數個月的公眾活動都被激進示威者騎劫，演變成暴力衝擊甚至暴動。明日遊行一旦有暴力事件發生，警方會暫停或中止遊行，警方亦準備了應變部署，有需要時會介入。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警務處處長鄧炳強昨日前往北京拜訪國務委員及公安部部長趙克志。趙克志表示，香港警察在修例風波以來盡忠履職，維護香港法治和社會大局穩定，重申止暴制亂、恢復秩序仍然是香港當前最緊迫的任務，希望鄧炳強能堅守初心，不負重託，強調中央政府和公安部永遠是香港警隊的強大後盾，堅定支持香港警隊嚴正執法。"},{"pid":"e13e35dfd718a3c9f076635a5644927856583c02","tid":1773000,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191207/large/1575648664_1774.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191207%2Flarge%2F1575648664_1774.gif&h=bf0a0cab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">遊行於明日下午2時在維園集合，3時出發，以中環遮打道行人專用區為終點。</span>"},{"pid":"ad96f2ca4d1f91e8968eeea6260090766e3f6049","tid":1773000,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:16:14.000Z","msg":"聽日見"},{"pid":"a199498aed3fab299f286d4f2ac446ad7eeceb71","tid":1773000,"uid":61405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:19:06.000Z","msg":"大家都睇定張不反通知書內容同規條先好去行 減少不必要的誤會 因為只要違反任何一條 佢都有權終止遊行"},{"pid":"b586c7918b1ff045a208f3f57990f02f73a9b0be","tid":1773000,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:19:22.000Z","msg":"聽日維園見"},{"pid":"1a48fdc67e7d85833347d78b0058c74ab091086d","tid":1773000,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:19:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/anc0Vqr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fanc0Vqr.png&h=07e546e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12點開始維園中央草坪有不反<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NQFqm5B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNQFqm5B.jpg&h=c075a8b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9747eaa4f5c2377a5042e6cac8c7589b93a56f72","tid":1773000,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:20:18.000Z","msg":"叫驚甴克制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e419aef6752a4117ab9939078b64215d750ec2c","tid":1773000,"uid":223678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:22:50.000Z","msg":"壽終正寢&mdash;-》撤回<br />\n檢討委員會&mdash;-》獨立調查員委員會？！"},{"pid":"313be4ec93c6e75b5ac5f873f66eed0fbacc8041","tid":1773000,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:24:57.000Z","msg":"【第十陸期牆紙】回首、向前<br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRHaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=958c6b81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768510/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768510/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AVwsVSd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAVwsVSd.jpg&h=bc013387&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"641dcb99872feeb4860ad0c5c12811e9596434ca","tid":1773000,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:27:31.000Z","msg":"民陣明遊行籲前線警克制<br />\n【#和你行不反已出,12.8維園見!】<br />\n<br />\n民陣12.8 國際人權日遊行已取得警方不反對通知書,是7.21<br />\n以來首次遊行獲批 8.18變成「流水式集會」,8.31、<br />\n10.1、10.20 幾次遊行申請皆被禁止。今次遊行也將将是區議會<br />\n選舉、人權法案通過後,最大的機會向國際社會表達香港人對<br />\n抗警暴、爭取民主的決心。<br />\n<br />\n香港人,星期日3點,維園見!<br />\n<br />\n不反對通知書時間:<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">維園中央草坪| 12-6 PM</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">遊行路線|3-10 PM</span><br />\n<br />\n【民陣 12.8 海報下載】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/3890Jq0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3890Jq0&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRHaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=74f779df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3890Jq0</a><br />\n<br />\n【巴丢草為12.8 遊行設計的海報】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2r5bSZj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2r5bSZj&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRHaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=3b6cd8e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2r5bSZj</a><br />\n<br />\n守護香港,和你同行| 12.8國際人權日遊行<br />\nStand With Hong Kong, Walk With You All:<br />\nHuman Rights Day Rally 2019<br />\n12.8 星期日Sunday | 3PM<br />\n維園中央草坪遊行至遮打道行人專用區<br />\nFrom Victoria Park (Central Lawn) to<br />\nChater Road Pedestrian Precinct<br />\n*已取得不反對通知書<br />\n*Letter of No Objection Received<br />\n<br />\n【民陣12.8 海報下載】 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/3890JqO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3890JqO&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRHaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=b2a7cccb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3890JqO</a><br />\n99 Full Statement <a href=\"http://bit.ly/204amPB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F204amPB&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRHaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=ffdfcc2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/204amPB</a><br />\n#守護香港 #和你同行<br />\n#五大訴求 #缺一不可<br />\n#StandUp4HumanRights"},{"pid":"c5f883baaefe3f4012b73571e74